cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with the automatic segmentation of brain MR images. It also involves the evaluation of different methods using various metrics, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of containerization and submission of methods to the challenge organizers suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Finally, the analysis of results and the use of multi-center/-scanner image dataset may also fall under multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
